  "takeaways": [
    "Best Ascend port targets: MiniMax-M3 (plain GQA → easiest on NPU, fast decode) + GLM-5.2 (MIT base for RL post-training); DeepSeek-V4 as the already-supported large rollout/eval baseline.",
